(13939, 'sodium chloride 0.9% w/v for intravenous infusion', 'N/A', 'moderate', 'Caution must be exercised in the administration of Sodium Chloride Injection, USP to patients receiving corticosteroids or corticotropin.', 'DailyMed'),
